MEMBERSHIP PERKS

Each Good Dood is unique and programmatically generated with over 10,000 gifts, including Raybans, Melin Hats, Super73 Electic Bikes, Tesla Cyberquads, Lego Spaceships, Apple Watches, Inspiration4 Space Puppies, and more. All Good Doods are givers, but some give more than others.

Good Doods are stored as SPL tokens on the Solana blockchain (keeping gas fees low) and hosted on IPFS. Purchasing a Good Dood costs 25 SOL.
